default11.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultEnrolment in the RHI req
defaultuires a Green Deal assessment, which requires an up-front fee and associates
default the RHI with a much-criticised,
default and (to date) 
defaultrelatively 
defaultunsuccessful initiative
default. It seems reasonable to expect
default that this will hamper its take up
default to some extent
default.  
